{"tid":883533,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"本港9月私樓售價按月跌幅擴大至1.4%　連跌兩月","createTime":"2018-10-31T02:17:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-31T12:54:16.000Z","uid":41404,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"600ba7d2c1ef7bcf85df972f23f0e8d7e296894e","tid":883533,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T02:17:00.000Z","msg":"本港9月樓價指數連跌兩個月，跌幅擴大至逾1%。<br />\n<br />\n差餉物業估價署公布，本港9月私人住宅售價指數報388.8，按月下跌1.4%，跌幅較8月的不足0.1%明顯擴大。<br />\n<br />\n指數在8月已結束連續28個月的升勢。<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1425775-20181031.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1425775-20181031.htm&d=NlEDQddTLS4quxxam7spjQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=b8c0b8ad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1425775-20181031.htm&h=ebc794a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1425775-20181031.htm</a>"},{"pid":"83aa8581cfd731e902fe7413e7e7b60751298c54","tid":883533,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T02:18:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6da29fbeb0f455fba853a0557cf8ed4bdd539824","tid":883533,"uid":77196,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T02:18:51.000Z","msg":"連升咗28個月，咁應該連跌28個月先叫新聞啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04a0eb30136b7a628ccc4491c2a5edc1def2d548","tid":883533,"uid":122377,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T02:21:40.000Z","msg":"下個月出10月表現 精彩囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50c645b5b9daf3c595aa29327d203501eca459c8","tid":883533,"uid":59283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T02:22:46.000Z","msg":"唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif